# AI/ML Program Health Check

A structured framework for early-stage AI/ML startups to identify success metrics, map risks, and build quality feedback loops.

## Who Is This For?

Founders and engineering leads at **MVP → early post-launch** stage AI/ML startups who need to answer:
- "How do I know if my AI is good enough?"
- "What should I measure?"
- "What's going to bite me before launch?"

## What's Included

### 📋 [Health Check Framework](framework/health_check_template.md)
One-page fillable template designed to be completed during a 45-minute discovery call. Covers:
- **Product Snapshot** — stage, team, AI core
- **Success Metrics** — output quality, business impact, performance, data quality
- **Risk Map** — data, model, evaluation, infra, timeline, team (rated 🟢🟡🔴)
- **Evaluation & Quality Loop** — automated eval, human review, feedback→retraining, regression detection
- **Responsible AI & Compliance** — bias, transparency, privacy, EU AI Act readiness
- **Launch Readiness** — 8 go/no-go signals
- **Top 3 Action Items** — highest-impact next steps

### 📊 [Launch Readiness Metrics Cheat Sheet](framework/launch_readiness_metrics.md)
Deep-dive companion with detailed metrics across business and technical dimensions:
- Output Quality (hallucination rate, toxicity, groundedness)
- Business Impact (retention, conversion, cost per inference, NPS)
- System Performance (latency, throughput, uptime)
- Data Pipeline (freshness, drift, labeling accuracy)
- Evaluation Loop (regression rate, human-AI agreement)
- Responsible AI (bias score, PII exposure, incident response)
- Launch Readiness Scorecard (🟢🟡🔴 summary)

### 🎙️ [Call Guide](call-guide/call_guide.md)
Script and structure for running the 45-minute health check session — opening, transitions, probing questions, time checks, and closing.

### 📝 [Example: Filled Template](examples/sample_filled.md)
A sample completed health check from a role-play exercise showing how the framework looks when filled in.

## How to Use

1. **Before the call:** Review the Health Check Framework and Call Guide
2. **During the call (45 min):** Walk through the framework together, fill it in live
3. **After the call:** Share the completed framework + Metrics Cheat Sheet as a follow-up

## Context

This framework was built from experience leading AI/ML programs at Amazon — including GenAI pipelines with 22+ ML classifiers, evaluation systems combining automated scoring with human-in-the-loop review, and IoT product launches with bilingual AI agents.

The Responsible AI section reflects the upcoming **EU AI Act** (full enforcement August 2, 2026) requirements for high-risk AI systems.

